{"tid":778270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麥當勞一連 16 日快閃優惠回歸！10蚊兩個豬柳漢堡","createTime":"2018-08-13T14:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T03:58:58.000Z","uid":179810,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c536419fbe8e2517d5beb498772bc3b31cc07c3a","tid":778270,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:30:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2135000/2135329/M02--_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2135000%2F2135329%2FM02--_1024.jpg&h=bd3764b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家期待已久的麥當勞「日日不同滋味快閃遊」優惠終於回歸了。今次的優惠跟以往差不多，都是天天不同，由 2018 年 8 月 13 日（星期一）到 8 月 28 日（星期二）一連 16 日為大家帶來驚喜。現時官方就只公佈了首 3 天優惠詳情，最平只需要 $10 就可以帶兩個豬柳漢堡或兩件香烤雞翼連中汽水回家。<br />\n<br />\n8月13日（星期一）：HK$10 兩個豬柳漢堡<br />\n8月14日（星期二）：HK$16 一個四重芝士孖堡 + 一杯中汽水<br />\n8月15日（星期三）：HK$10 兩件香烤雞翼 + 一杯細汽水<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2135000/2135329/M3_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2135000%2F2135329%2FM3_600.jpg&h=7adfaf8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n8月頭新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無藥可治！中國爆非洲豬瘟 已撲殺三八三頭染病豬隻 全台防堵<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/btOPvS\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/btOPvS</a>"},{"pid":"b92b8a5dea22bdb5abbaddf35e53a17891c69f20","tid":778270,"uid":20867,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:38:48.000Z","msg":"#9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國爆非洲豬瘟 冷凍豬病毒可活一千天<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/769795\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/769795</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"00e451be7c2109d6c59680e3d380b53a2b19